cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.IR, cs.NE 

This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category of natural language processing (cs.CL) because it proposes a model for inducing meaning representations for words. It could also belong to machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) because it involves training a model to learn representations. Information retrieval (cs.IR) is another possible sub-category because word embeddings are often used in information retrieval tasks. Finally, neural networks (cs.NE) could also be a relevant sub-category because the proposed model likely involves the use of neural networks.
